So, I was very nervous about it--
Coming here, so--

01:09:41.093 --> 01:09:43.261
I'm not the sort of person
to be nervous about.

01:09:43.345 --> 01:09:44.470
No, not at all, but--

01:09:44.555 --> 01:09:46.515
-Yeah.
-I guess I just wanna hear

01:09:46.599 --> 01:09:49.894
