I will.

01:11:01.465 --> 01:11:02.967
-Because we have to.
-Absolutely.

01:11:03.050 --> 01:11:05.552
We've got no choice.
You've got no choice, I'm afraid.

01:11:05.636 --> 01:11:07.721
-You've gotta keep at it. You've got to.
-Yep, yep.

01:11:08.305 --> 01:11:11.475
