I think having been on the journey
that I've been on,

01:22:50.465 --> 01:22:53.093
I should be the most depressed person
on the planet.

01:22:53.176 --> 01:22:54.511
I'm seeing the ecosystem

01:22:54.594 --> 01:22:56.262
that I've fallen in love with...

01:22:56.680 --> 01:22:58.014
